&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.openscenegraph.org/projects/osg/attachment/wiki/Support/PlatformSpecifics/VisualStudio/VisualStudioPlugins/vrml_sample2.zip&quot; title=&quot;View attachment&quot; style=&quot;color: #bb0000; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: #bbbbbb;&quot;&gt;vrml_sample2.zip&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;span title=&quot;49453 bytes&quot;&gt;48.3 kB&lt;/span&gt;) - added by &lt;em&gt;janoc&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;timeline&quot; href=&quot;http://www.openscenegraph.org/projects/osg/timeline?from=2009-05-26T13%3A46%3A59Z%2B0200&amp;amp;precision=second&quot; title=&quot;2009-05-26T13:46:59Z+0200 in Timeline&quot; style=&quot;color: #bb0000; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: #bbbbbb;&quot;&gt;3 years&lt;/a&gt; ago. &lt;q&gt;VRML test files, includes &lt;a class=&quot;missing wiki&quot; href=&quot;http://www.openscenegraph.org/projects/osg/wiki/IndexedFaceSet&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; style=&quot;color: #999988; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: #bbbbbb; background-color: #fafaf0;&quot;&gt;IndexedFaceSet?&lt;/a&gt;, primitives and textured surface&lt;/q&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
